channel.title: I Need Help With Josh's HD 508 Client Ip Changer and a Hd Server
channel.description:
Ok well i download this server from moparscape server downloads:http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,416977.0.html and its a 508 hd server. So i downloaded the source and the client, then i opened the "run" file and once i open it says "starting server on port: 43594" so i thought that was alright, then i open the Josh's HD 508 Client Ip Changer client and run it. I typed in the ip "0.0.0.0" then pressed the enter key. I was thinking it was all fine and dandy. So once it was running it wasnt doing anything. So i looked at the source that was running and it said "connection recieved from: 192.168.1.3" it said that 4 times then it started saying "currently 0 players online!" and it has said that 14 times and is still saying it :eek:. So i looked at the "run.bat" that was open and it said "error_game_js5io". So i don't know what to do with this, can anybody help me? please :confused:
Diablo Runes
